cornflakes.lang

Class Pointer

  • java.lang.Object
    • cornflakes.lang.Pointer
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    BoolPointer, CharPointer, F32Pointer, F64Pointer, I16Pointer, I32Pointer, I64Pointer, I8Pointer, ObjectPointer

    public abstract class Pointer
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
    The Pointer class is the superclass type for all Cornflakes pointer wrapper classes. It contains several static methods for creating pointers.
    Author:
    Lucas Baizer
    See Also:
    Serialized Form
